-- Microsoft Seeks End to Dinosaur-Era Upgrade Cycle
-- B y
-- 2013-06-27T18:30:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-27/microsoft-seeks-end-to-dinosaur-era-upgrade-cycle.html
Microsoft, which for decades has 
refreshed its popular Office corporate software just once about 
every three years, says it will soon switch to weekly updates. 
Cory Johnson reports on Bloomberg Television's "Bloomberg 
West." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 02:00
 